brain-cancer-detection/
│
├── README.md                # Short project overview & setup instructions
├── requirements.txt         # Dependencies (tensorflow, opencv, scikit-learn)
│
├── data/
│   ├── raw/                 # Original MRI scans
│   └── splits/              # Train/validation/test split folders
│
├── notebooks/
│   ├── 01_EDA.ipynb         # Explore dataset (visualize MRI scans, class balance)
│   └── 02_model.ipynb       # Build & train CNN (or transfer learning)
│
├── src/
│   ├── data_loader.py       # Load/preprocess MRI images
│   └── model.py             # CNN or transfer learning model
│
├── models/
│   └── final_model.h5       # Saved trained model
│
└── dockerfile (optional)    # Only if you want deployment later